name: This The Air That I Breathe
chorusText:
This is the air I breathe
This is the air I breathe
Your Holy pre—sence
Living   -- in me
This is my daily bread
This is my daily bread
You’re every w—ord 
Spoken  -- to me
And I……I’m desperate for you
And I……I’m desperate for you

And I……I’m lost without you
And I……I’m lost without you
